   How can I calculate with big numbers. The normal types on my machine are 
   only up to 2^32-1. But I need to work with very large numbers, up to
   200 or 500 digits and more!!

   How can I do it?

Find yourself a bignum package.  Such packages include (but are not
limited to) MPI, LIP, and GMP.  You milage may very.

